title: Spider-Man and Ant Man
body:
I like to imagine that Peter and Scott would get along quite well with each other. 

Both of them are very approachable to others, along with being the two underdogs of the MCU films. There is also the fact that both are themed after arthropods.

For me, I picture most of their conversations being rather light-hearted, and I also imagine that Scott would offer plenty of advice to Peter in some matters in daily life.

In short, they seem like they would be very good friends. ^_^

If anyone would like to leave a comment on what their interactions would be like, feel free to do so.
